#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.220"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.220:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.220:0.2"
msgid "21. Karajakāyavagga "
msgstr "21. The Body Born of Deeds "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.220:0.3"
msgid "220. Adhammacariyāsutta "
msgstr "220. Unprincipled Conduct "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.220:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then a certain brahmin went up to the Buddha and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "an10.220:1.2"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side and said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.220:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bho gotama, hetu ko paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjantī”ti? "
msgstr "“What is the cause, Master Gotama, what is the reason why some sentient beings, when their body breaks up, after death, are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.220:1.4"
msgid "“Adhammacariyāvisamacariyāhetu kho, brāhmaṇa, evam’idhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjantī”ti. "
msgstr "“Unprincipled and immoral conduct is the reason why some sentient beings, when their body breaks up, after death, are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.302, sc2
msgctxt "an10.220:2.1"
msgid "“Ko pana, bho gotama, hetu ko paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjantī”ti? "
msgstr "“But what is the cause, Master Gotama, what is the reason why some sentient beings, when their body breaks up, after death, are reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.220:2.2"
msgid "“Dhammacariyāsamacariyāhetu kho, brāhmaṇa, evam’idhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjantī”ti. "
msgstr "“Principled and moral conduct is the reason why some sentient beings, when their body breaks up, after death, are reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an10.220:3.1"
msgid "“Na kho ahaṃ imassa bhoto gotamassa saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmi. "
msgstr "“I don’t understand the detailed meaning of what Master Gotama has said in brief. "

msgctxt "an10.220:3.2"
msgid "Sādhu me bhavaṃ gotamo tathā dhammaṃ desetu yathāhaṃ imassa bhoto gotamassa saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ ājāneyyan”ti. "
msgstr "Please, Master Gotama, teach me this matter so I can understand the detailed meaning.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.220:3.3"
msgid "“Tena hi, brāhmaṇa, suṇāhi, sādhukaṃ manasi karohi; bhāsissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "“Well then, brahmin, listen and pay close attention, I will speak.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.220:3.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bho”ti kho so brāhmaṇo bhagavato paccassosi. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” the brahmin replied. "

msgctxt "an10.220:3.5"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.220:4.1"
msgid "“Tividhā kho, brāhmaṇa, kāyena adhammacariyāvisamacariyā hoti; "
msgstr "“Brahmin, unprincipled and immoral conduct is threefold by way of body, "

msgctxt "an10.220:4.2"
msgid "catubbidhā vācāya adhammacariyāvisamacariyā hoti; "
msgstr "fourfold by way of speech, "

msgctxt "an10.220:4.3"
msgid "tividhā manasā adhammacariyāvisamacariyā hoti. "
msgstr "and threefold by way of mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an10.220:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, brāhmaṇa, tividhā kāyena adhammacariyāvisamacariyā hoti … pe … "
msgstr "And how is unprincipled and immoral conduct threefold by way of body? … "

msgctxt "an10.220:5.2"
msgid "evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, tividhā kāyena adhammacariyā visamacariyā hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how unprincipled and immoral conduct is threefold by way of body. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an10.220:6.1"
msgid "Kathañca, brāhmaṇa, catubbidhā vācāya adhammacariyāvisamacariyā hoti … pe … "
msgstr "And how is unprincipled and immoral conduct fourfold by way of speech? … "

msgctxt "an10.220:6.2"
msgid "evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, catubbidhā vācāya adhammacariyāvisamacariyā hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how unprincipled and immoral conduct is fourfold by way of speech. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an10.220:7.1"
msgid "Kathañca, brāhmaṇa, tividhā manasā adhammacariyāvisamacariyā hoti … pe … "
msgstr "And how is unprincipled and immoral conduct threefold by way of mind? … "

msgctxt "an10.220:7.2"
msgid "evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, tividhā manasā adhammacariyāvisamacariyā hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how unprincipled and immoral conduct is threefold by way of mind. "

msgctxt "an10.220:7.3"
msgid "Evaṃ adhammacariyāvisamacariyāhetu kho, brāhmaṇa, evam’idhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjanti. "
msgstr "That’s how unprincipled and immoral conduct is the reason why some sentient beings, when their body breaks up, after death, are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an10.220:8.1"
msgid "Tividhā, brāhmaṇa, kāyena dhammacariyāsamacariyā hoti; "
msgstr "Principled and moral conduct is threefold by way of body, "

msgctxt "an10.220:8.2"
msgid "catubbidhā vācāya dhammacariyāsamacariyā hoti; "
msgstr "fourfold by way of speech, "

msgctxt "an10.220:8.3"
msgid "tividhā manasā dhammacariyāsamacariyā hoti. "
msgstr "and threefold by way of mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.303, sc9
msgctxt "an10.220:9.1"
msgid "Kathañca, brāhmaṇa, tividhā kāyena dhammacariyāsamacariyā hoti … pe … "
msgstr "And how is principled and moral conduct threefold by way of body? … "

msgctxt "an10.220:9.2"
msgid "evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, tividhā kāyena dhammacariyāsamacariyā hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how principled and moral conduct is threefold by way of body. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an10.220:10.1"
msgid "Kathañca, brāhmaṇa, catubbidhā vācāya dhammacariyāsamacariyā hoti … pe … "
msgstr "And how is principled and moral conduct fourfold by way of speech? … "

msgctxt "an10.220:10.2"
msgid "evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, catubbidhā vācāya dhammacariyāsamacariyā hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how principled and moral conduct is fourfold by way of speech. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an10.220:11.1"
msgid "Kathañca, brāhmaṇa, tividhā manasā dhammacariyāsamacariyā hoti … pe … "
msgstr "And how is principled and moral conduct threefold by way of mind? … "

msgctxt "an10.220:11.2"
msgid "evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, tividhā manasā dhammacariyāsamacariyā hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how principled and moral conduct is threefold by way of mind. "

msgctxt "an10.220:11.3"
msgid "Evaṃ dhammacariyāsamacariyāhetu kho, brāhmaṇa, evam’idhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjantī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how principled and moral conduct is the reason why some sentient beings, when their body breaks up, after death, are reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "an10.220:12.1"
msgid "“Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! … "

msgctxt "an10.220:12.2"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.220:12.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.220:12.4"
msgid "Karajakāyavaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr ""

